    "Pro tip: each saved macro can also have its OWN hotkey from the card menu — set one and that macro plays from anywhere.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pro tip: each saved macro can also have its OWN hotkey from the card menu — set one and that macro plays from anywhere."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "提示：每个已保存宏都能在卡片菜单设置自己的快捷键，设置后可从任意位置播放。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Click the menu-bar icon or this Dock icon to open the library. Press Record to capture your first macro — recording starts immediately.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
